      You belong [B]with me<br>
      [Q]Standing by and waiting at your back door [N]All this time how could you not [W]know, baby <br>
      You belong with me, [B]you belong with me
    </p>
    <p>
      I got my [Q] hands up They're [V] playing my song, I [M] know I'm gonna be o-[N]kay<br>
      [Q] Yeah [V], it's a [M] party in the US-[N]A<br>
      [Q] Yeah [V], it's a [M] party in the US-[N]A
    </p>
