    <p>[Q]Country roads, take me [N]home To the [M]place I [B]belong</p>
  </div>
  <div id="click_to_start">
    <h2>Click to Start</h2>
    <p>Due to Web Audio autoplay limitation you need to click the button before we can start.</p>
    <button class="ui button" onclick="clickStart();">Start</button>
  </div>
